{"word":"G3800 - ὀψώνιον - opsṓnion - op-so'-nee-on - Wages","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὀψώνιον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>opsṓnion"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>op-so'-nee-on"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Wages"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"சம்பளம், பணம் - பால் வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. a soldier's pay, allowance"},{"paragraph":"2. wages"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Neuter of a presumed derivative of the same as <a href=\"#/G3795 - ὀψάριον - opsárion - op-sar'-ee-on/3795\">G3795</a>; <i>rations</i> for a soldier, that is, (by extension) his <i>stipend</i> or <i>pay:</i> - wages."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}